非常了解，由於當時街上傳出催淚彈氣味，加上有大批食客仍在餐廳內進食，當中不少是家長帶同小朋友在內，於是決定即時下半閘，待所有食客離開後才正式提早暫停關門。據知，該經理拒絕警員入內的主要原因，是害怕令場內的小朋友被嚇到。<br />\n<br />\n而有網上影片拍到，防暴警進入店內後，有餐廳內進食中的小朋友被嚇哭。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10AJ6nn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10AJ6nn.jpg&h=cf125c01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uS7Ac2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuS7Ac2p.jpg&h=6e02ed5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aaronMCN/status/1193512000728354816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FaaronMCN%2Fstatus%2F1193512000728354816&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=ed238922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FaaronMCN%2Fstatus%2F1193512000728354816&h=1691ab19\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/aaronMCN/status/1193512000728354816</a>"},{"pid":"248dcdd54ea67848426a87f2803ffb459a2a4173","tid":1703994,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b04845e15ed1aa57559ee3c63400d57350267851","tid":1703994,"uid":53016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>麥當勞分店經理疑免餐廳內幼童嚇怕 拒防暴警搜查被捕</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/396805/11-10-%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E7%96%91%E5%85%8D%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E5%85%A7%E5%B9%BC%E7%AB%A5%E5%9A%87%E6%80%95-%E6%8B%92%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%90%9C%E6%9F%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F396805%2F11-10-%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2585%258D%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25B9%25